::Sorry, I must have misread.  But I'm not talking specifically about your proposal, I'm talking about the idea in general, as have the above 30+ comments.  Hence why I listed it here.  —[[User:Bbatsell|<b><font color="#555">bbatsell</font></b>]] [[User_talk:Bbatsell|<font color="#C46100" size="1">¿?</font>]] [[Special:Contributions/Bbatsell|<font color="#2C9191" size="3">✍</font>]] 19:08, 9 March 2007 (UTC)
