== Proposed policy: Template prod ==

:''This was announced at Village pump (proposals) but is seemed good to announce it here too.''
From a discussion at Wikipedia talk:Templates for deletion I have created a draft policy for situations in which templates may be proposed for deletion.  Please see [[Wikipedia:Proposed deletion/Template prod]] and discuss it at [[Wikipedia talk:Proposed deletion/Template prod]].  Thank you.  <font face="monospace">[[User:Dgies|<font color="#00F">'''&mdash;dgies'''</font>]]<sup>[[User talk:Dgies|t]]</sup><sub>[[Special:Contributions/Dgies|c]]</sub></font> 18:02, 16 March 2007 (UTC)
